---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Cara Colgate, LICSW" currentPage="home">
  <div class="hero-image">
    <img
      src="/images/hero-path.jpg"
      alt="A winding wooden boardwalk through green marshland under a dramatic sky"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="home-content">
    <p>
      When people feel better, they do better. This is true whether you are overwhelmed by
      challenges at work, school or home, have a child who is struggling socially or academically,
      or simply find that your life is not going how you had hoped or expected. Therapy is an
      opportunity to address specific challenges and to build skills that can lead a more fulfilling
      life. It can help you, and those you care for, feel and do better.
    </p>

    <p>
      I have over 20 years of experience helping adults, families and children, and remain
      passionate about my work. My approach is warm, collaborative and appropriately challenging.
      I believe that there is no "perfect" method to solve all of life's challenges because people
      and families are all unique. Instead, I employ a variety of strategies in my work, including
      cognitive behavioral therapy and psychodynamic (insight-oriented) therapy, that best fit your
      individual strengths and struggles.
    </p>

    <p>
      Please <a href="/connect/">reach out</a> to discuss how working together might help.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero-image {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 260px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 40%;
  }

  .home-content {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .home-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .home-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
